metatags.title: Disneyland® Hotel Hotel - Chessy - France - With 5 guest reviews
metatags.og:title: Disneyland® Hotel Hotel - Chessy - France - With 5 guest reviews
metatags.og:description: Location. Inspired by the grandeur of Victorian mansions, this 5-star Disney hotel  stands right by the entrance gates to Disneyland® Park.  Disney Village, with shopping, dining, and entertainment, is a 3-minute walk. Paris is about 30 minutes away via train. Disneyland® Hotel provides complimentary shuttle service to the theme park and the Marne-la-Vallée-Chessy train station, about a 2-minute ride.    Hotel Features.   Children can meet and greet popular Disney characters, with lots of photo opportunities. A complimentary Continental breakfast buffet is served each morning. For recreation and relaxation, the hotel offers an indoor pool, spa tub, sauna, steam room, and gym, along with the new, full-service Celestia Spa, offering face and body treatments, massages, and manicures and pedicures. A golf course and tennis courts also are available. Dining options include Inventions restaurant, serving international buffets, and the California Grill, showcasing gourmet foods and fine wines.
